results.name: Guild Wars 2 UnknownSuperficialDarkness-Custom-version
results.description: This is my custom version of gw2 from Launch_taco script
results.notes: This version is slightly modified for better performance and no shader cache so you can generate your own
results.content:
files:
- gw2installer: https://s3.amazonaws.com/gw2cdn/client/branches/Gw2Setup-64.exe
-  arch: win64
  exe: drive_c/Program Files/Guild Wars 2/GW2-64.exe
  prefix: $GAMEDIR
installer:
- arch: win64
    description: Running Guild Wars 2 Installer.
    executable: gw2installer
    name: wineexec
    prefix: $GAMEDIR
system:
  env:
    __GL_SHADER_DISK_CACHE: 1
    __GL_SHADER_DISK_CACHE_PATH: $GAMEDIR
  pulse_latency: true
wine:
  dxvk: true
  esync: true
 fsync: true
 version: lutris-fshack-7.2-x86_64
